### ========== 启动类 Program.cs 中切换 AuthDemoMode ==========
### Classic         → 下面「原 Demo」接口
### DynamicSession  → 下面「DynamicClaims」接口

### ========== 原 Demo：Cookie（AuthDemoMode.Classic）==========

### Cookie 登录
POST {{Authentication_jwt_cookie_HostAddress}}/Auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "admin",
  "password": "123456"
}

### Cookie 登出
POST {{Authentication_jwt_cookie_HostAddress}}/Auth/logout

### Cookie 认证 - 获取用户列表
GET {{Authentication_jwt_cookie_HostAddress}}/User

### ========== 原 Demo：JWT（AuthDemoMode.Classic）==========

### JWT 登录
POST {{Authentication_jwt_cookie_HostAddress}}/JwtAuth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "admin",
  "password": "123456"
}

### JWT 认证 - 获取商品（需替换 {{token}}）
GET {{Authentication_jwt_cookie_HostAddress}}/Product/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Cookie 认证 - 获取商品（登录后 Cookie 自动携带）
GET {{Authentication_jwt_cookie_HostAddress}}/Product/1

### ========== DynamicClaims Demo（AuthDemoMode.DynamicSession）==========

### 1. 登录（返回含 session_id 的 token，角色快照 Admin+User）
POST {{Authentication_jwt_cookie_HostAddress}}/dynamic-claims/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "admin",
  "password": "123456"
}

### 2. 查看当前身份（经 Dynamic Claims 覆盖后的 roles）
GET {{Authentication_jwt_cookie_HostAddress}}/dynamic-claims/me
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 3. Admin 专属（未改角色前应 200）
GET {{Authentication_jwt_cookie_HostAddress}}/dynamic-claims/admin-only
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 4. 热更新角色：去掉 Admin（Token 不用换）
PUT {{Authentication_jwt_cookie_HostAddress}}/dynamic-claims/users/admin/roles
Content-Type: application/json

["User"]

### 5. 再看 me → roles 只有 User；admin-only → 403
GET {{Authentication_jwt_cookie_HostAddress}}/dynamic-claims/me
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

GET {{Authentication_jwt_cookie_HostAddress}}/dynamic-claims/admin-only
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 6. 撤销当前会话 → 再访问 me → 401
POST {{Authentication_jwt_cookie_HostAddress}}/dynamic-claims/logout
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

GET {{Authentication_jwt_cookie_HostAddress}}/dynamic-claims/me
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
